Text: Hi. This is Tommy calling about my mom's arthritis
prescription. The new one she started last Tuesday.
She's been saying her ankles are really puffy,
I mean, She's always had some swelling, but this seems different.
She's also on water pills for her heart. So I'm
not sure if it's related to those or the new med. Oh,
and she mentioned feeling a bit under the weather. Could
you have the pharmacist to call me back? Thanks.
